{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A lite roguelike card deck building game inspired by Slay the Spire. You can experience battles of robots with cards and components!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263280/extras/\u5546\u5e97\u9875\u5185\u5bb9\u4ecb\u7ecd\u56fe_EN.png?t=1731296170\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Turn-Based Card Battle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will draw cards at the beginning of your turn and regenerate energy. Make smart and precise decision on energy consumption and cards to play, you will need to be flexible among Attack cards, Defend cards and Ability Cards to fight against enemies' attack and skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263280/extras/battle.gif?t=1731296170\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Classic Roguelike Deck Building</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you have played Slay the Spire, you are already familiar with all the basic rules of this game. All the classic designs are reserved. You can start with some basic cards, defeat enemies to collect new powerful cards and components to build you own deck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263280/extras/map.gif?t=1731296170\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A New Way To Start</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We like Hearth Stone Arena mode, if you enjoy it, you can start the game with a card selection process. Every round, you choose 1 card from 3, after 8 rounds, you will have your initial customized beginning deck!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>High Difficulty Boss Fight</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Boss fight should not be hard in terms of super high damage or HP, it should be hard in a more interesting way. We have designed 5 Bosses with special abilities you need to learn to kill it.\u00a0</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263280/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731296170","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263280/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731296170","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263280/c932a3df773e4d8c6d0fd8015c559d81097bc610/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731296170","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263280/c932a3df773e4d8c6d0fd8015c559d81097bc610/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731296170","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A lite roguelike card deck building game inspired by Slay the Spire. You can experience battles of robots with cards and components!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263280/extras/\u5546\u5e97\u9875\u5185\u5bb9\u4ecb\u7ecd\u56fe_EN.png?t=1731296170\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Turn-Based Card Battle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will draw cards at the beginning of your turn and regenerate energy. Make smart and precise decision on energy consumption and cards to play, you will need to be flexible among Attack cards, Defend cards and Ability Cards to fight against enemies' attack and skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263280/extras/battle.gif?t=1731296170\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Classic Roguelike Deck Building</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you have played Slay the Spire, you are already familiar with all the basic rules of this game. All the classic designs are reserved. You can start with some basic cards, defeat en